trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for editing the collection of cells in a table row.
trans-unit.target: Gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering samling av celler i en tabell.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TableCellsCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TableCellsCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The type of the collection to edit.
Indicates whether multiple table cells can be selected at the same time.
trans-unit.target: Angir om flere celler kan velges samtidig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if multiple cells can be selected at the same time; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis du kan velge flere celler samtidig; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the editor for use with the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av redigeringsprogrammet for bruk med den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the item to create.
An object of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt av den angitte typen.
